data.description:
NEW PICTURES WILL COME ONCE NEW CARPET IS INSTALLED!This beautifully custom-built home is like no other! Located at the end of a cul-de-sac, this home boasts privacy & space! As one enters this home to the left is a flex room, to the right a formal dining area. Continue through an exceptionally large living room area with trey ceilings. The additional dining area continues through to an oversized kitchen with birch cabinets, black granite, stainless steel appliances, raised bar, & island! Additionally, the well sized primary bedroom connects to primary bathroom which has separate sinks, garden jacuzzi tub, large custom shower, & closet with built ins! Continue through the additional bedrooms, bathrooms, and a huge bonus area upstairs! The home offers a 3-car garage, and a fully fenced large backyard, as well as a pergola area perfect for entertaining!
Upgrades in this home include, a tesla charger, new carpets downstairs, Rachio Smart Sprinkler system, Ecobee Thermostat, Ring Alarm sensors on all entry points as well as most windows, Arlo Doorbell Camera and floodlight camera, touch activated kitchen sink, new shower heads in primary bathroom and additional bathroom, brand new AC unit in upstairs bonus room!

BUYER TO VERIFY ALL INFORMATION PROVIDED.
